Program: Discovery
Title: Nanotechnology - part three
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryj7
Last Broadcast Date: 21 October 2003
Report on the advancements in nano technology. As the technology gets smaller and smaller the programme looks at the serious business of nanotechnology and its use in computing. Four decades of ever-shrinking improvements have however come at a price and the time has come for a new approach.